_sText:
A medium sized map created over the course of about 3 hours. Still in alpha mode, so I'm open to suggestions. I've already started working on a new version of this one, but it's completely different so I think I'm going to branch them apart. :P

Please do not edit or redistribute without expressed consent from the original author (me.)

Features:
-50 spawn points
-Custom 3d skybox
-Custom lighting
-Buyzones
-Nav file included!
